Players.

Use players to list other visible players in your current room.

The command does not include you in the list. It only reports other player
characters that you can currently see.

Common forms:

players
  List other visible players in the room.

look <player>
  Look more closely at a player from the list.

say <message>
  Speak to everyone in the room.

tell <player> <message>
  Send a private message to a player.

Invisible players or players hidden from you may not appear.
